Basketball (College)
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Khadijah Rushdan and Monique Oliver each scored 15 points to help No. 15 Rutgers beat visiting Boston College, 74-58. Rutgers (2-0) jumped out to a 13-2 lead against the Eagles (1-1).
